# Exclude bulky / dev-only / sensitive files from the Docker build context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/web/dist
**/server/dist
# v0.9.55 — keep the prebuilt HACS card bundles in the build context.
# `**/dist` above would have excluded these; Docker honours later negations.
!lovelace/dist
!lovelace/dist/**
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.production
**/*.log
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
data/
launchd/
.claude/
README.md
DOCS.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
